race.comment: Very weak maiden and if HAPPY WINS (7) lines up here should be tough to beat. Also engaged in town but would surely go close this line-up on two solid runs before a good break. Fitter for two trial and looks a perfect assignment to open winning account. BUBBLE WARRIOR (5) is a Melissa Kelly trained three-year-old gelding lining up for first race start. Has had four trials in total, two this time in in, winning the latest comfortably. Showing ability and well educated and with the blinkers on should measure up. RAZOR'S MAGIC (8) finished fourth two runs back then did well last start but found a couple better over 1200m at this track, beaten only one length. Has her share of talent. Hard to beat in this suitable race.  ATHOL MAC (1) is close to a win and gets chance.
